      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'DecomStress - Inanna, Vega, Candy, Whitney



    We plan to combine a
    hacked fidget-toy controller with a stress induced environment to see if fidget
    toys really work!



    Squeeze different inputs to see your player move! Try
    different combinations and pressure levels to sneak up on the mouse!



    By
    introducing this new controller, the way we engage with a simple game and the
    controller itself is reshaped, challenging conventional playstyles in the process.
    We know it isn''t very stressful at the moment, but let us know what you think!'
